      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/11/57",
      "text": [
        "هِ ثُمَّ يُكَالُ مَا بَقِيَ عَلَى حِسَابِ ذَلِكَ مِنَ اَلْعَدَدِ قَالَ \"لاَ بَأْسَ بِهِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3828 - Hammad narrated from Al-Halabi, from Abu Abdullah (as):\nHe was asked about walnuts that cannot be counted individually, so they are measured with a container and then counted based on the amount in that container. Afterward, the remaining quantity is measured according to that count.\nImam (as) said: \"There is no problem with that.\""
        ]
      }
    },
